sub_questions: Which records have Year greater than 2006?
Which records have Developer equal to '3G Studios'?
What is the Platform value for records matching both conditions?

format_notes: Year column contains string values that need conversion to numeric for comparison
Platform column may contain multiple platforms separated by commas for some games

constraints: Year must be convertible to integer for comparison
Developer string match must be exact or case-insensitive
derived_filters: Convert Year column from string to integer before applying Year > 2006 filter
output_format_requirements: Return the Platform value as a string
If no records match, return null or empty result
If multiple records match, return all matching Platform values
